            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000171": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000171",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000172": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000172",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal c10\">Individual symbols are interpreted only when they either don’t make as much sense literally, or the resulting sentence would be awkward in English.  In some cases, if a symbol means two English words that both seem to fit equally well, they are combined into one phrase, such as “heart/mind” for <span class=\"c9\">心</span> <span></span>(see the next section), or <span class=\"c9\">玄</span> which can mean “mystery”, “profound”, “deep”, or “dark”, and is consistently translated as “deep and mysterious” or “deep mystery”, depending on the context.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000173": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000173",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000174": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000174",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000175": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000175",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000176": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000176",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\">The above goals hopefully help minimize, but cannot eliminate, translator bias.  The problem is that each Chinese symbol still has several meanings, and the translator must pick just one for each symbol (step 3) to create an English sentence that makes sense (step 4).  It is impossible to avoid translator bias here because the translator must choose what makes sense or feels right to them, in both word meanings and overall grammar.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000177": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000177",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000178": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000178",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000179": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000179",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000180": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000180",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal c10\">For example, there is a line in chapter 58 :  <span class=\"c9\">禍</span> <span></span><span class=\"c9\">兮</span> <span></span><span class=\"c9\">福</span> <span></span><span class=\"c9\">之</span> <span></span><span class=\"c9\">所</span> <span></span><span class=\"c9\">倚</span> where <span class=\"c9\">兮</span> can mean “good fortune” or “happiness” and <span class=\"c9\">禍</span> can mean “misfortune” or “disaster”, but by reflection with <span class=\"c9\">兮</span> could also be interpreted as “unhappiness”.  <span class=\"c9\">倚</span> can mean “lean on”, “rely on”, or “depend on”, so all of these are valid translations :</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000181": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000181",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000182": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000182",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal c11\">Misfortune is that which good fortune leans on.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000183": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000183",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000184": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000184",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal c11\">Misfortune is that which good fortune relies on.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000185": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000185",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000186": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000186",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal c11\">Misfortune is that which good fortune depends on.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000187": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000187",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000188": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000188",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal c11\">Unhappiness is that which happiness leans on.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000189": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000189",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000190": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000190",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal c11\">Unhappiness is that which happiness relies on.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000191": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000191",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000192": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000192",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal c11\">Unhappiness is that which happiness depends on.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000193": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000193",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000194": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000194",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000195": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000195",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000196": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000196",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Beyond the differences between using “fortune” (less personal : what happens to you) versus “happiness” (more personal : how you feel), there are also subtle differences : saying that one “relies” on the other is different than saying that they mutually support each other (as possibly indicated by the sentence following this one, not shown here).   </p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000197": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000197",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000198": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000198",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal c10\"> </p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000199": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000199",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000200": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000200",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal c10\">Unlike the previous example, where the different translations for each symbol are more-or-less related, sometimes the choice the translator makes can affect the overall meaning or even the emotional impact of the sentence.  In chapter 20, there is a line : <span class=\"c9\">我</span> <span></span><span class=\"c9\">獨</span> <span></span><span class=\"c9\">若</span> <span></span><span class=\"c9\">遺</span> <span class=\"c12\"></span>in which the last symbol can be variously translated into :</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000201": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000201",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000202": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000202",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal c11\">I alone seem lost.                   </p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000203": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000203",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000204": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000204",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal c11\">I alone seem to have lost everything.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000205": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000205",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000206": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000206",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal c11\">I alone seem to have been left behind.          </p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000207": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000207",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000208": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000208",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal c11\">I alone seem to be forgotten.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000209": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000209",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000210": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000210",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal c10\">Each of which says a completely different thing.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000211": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000211",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000212": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000212",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal c10\"> </p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000213": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000213",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000214": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000214",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal c10\">And in chapter 46, there is a line : <span class=\"c9\">罪</span> <span></span><span class=\"c9\">莫</span> <span></span><span class=\"c9\">大</span> <span></span><span class=\"c9\">於</span> <span></span><span class=\"c9\">可</span> <span></span><span class=\"c9\">欲</span> where the first symbol can mean any of : “sin”, “crime”, “vice”, or “fault”, so (ignoring options for the other symbols), all of these are valid :</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000215": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000215",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000216": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000216",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal c13\">There is no sin greater than the capacity for desire.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000217": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000217",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000218": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000218",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal c13\">There is no crime greater than the capacity for desire.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000219": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000219",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000220": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000220",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal c13\">There is no vice greater than the capacity for desire.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000221": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000221",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000222": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000222",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal c13\">There is no fault greater than the capacity for desire.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000223": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000223",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000224": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000224",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\">“Sin” of course has very negative religious connotations in the West, while “crime” and “vice” also have stronger negative associations than “fault”. </p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000225": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000225",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000226": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000226",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000227": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000227",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000228": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000228",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal c10\">But there are other, even more significant ways in which the translator’s choices affect the result.  Because of the many (sometimes unrelated) possible meanings of each Chinese symbol, it is possible to come up with multiple translations of the exact same sentence that are completely different in meaning!  For example, in chapter 41, there is a line : <span class=\"c9\">大</span> <span></span><span class=\"c9\">方</span> <span></span><span class=\"c9\">無</span> <span></span><span class=\"c9\">隅</span> where <span class=\"c9\">方</span> can mean both “region” and “square”, while <span class=\"c9\">隅</span> can be “border” or “corner”, so both of these are valid translations :</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000229": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000229",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000230": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000230",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal c13\">The greatest region is without borders.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000231": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000231",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000232": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000232",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal c13\">The greatest square is without corners.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000233": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000233",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000234": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000234",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000235": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000235",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000236": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000236",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal c10\">And in chapter 45 : <span class=\"c9\">大</span> <span></span><span class=\"c9\">巧</span> <span></span><span class=\"c9\">若</span> <span></span><span class=\"c9\">拙</span> where <span class=\"c9\">巧</span> can be “skillful” or “clever”, and <span class=\"c9\">拙</span> can mean “stupid” or “clumsy”, both of these are equally likely :</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000237": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000237",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000238": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000238",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal c13\">Great skillfulness seems clumsy.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000239": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000239",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000240": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000240",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal c13\">Great cleverness seems stupid.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000241": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000241",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000242": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000242",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000243": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000243",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000244": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000244",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal c10\">Finally, even when there is no ambiguity about the meaning of the individual symbols, it sometimes hard to determine what overall meaning was intended.  From chapter 35, there is a line : <span class=\"c9\">道</span> <span></span><span class=\"c9\">之</span> <span></span><span class=\"c9\">出</span> <span></span><span class=\"c9\">言</span> <span></span><span class=\"c9\">淡</span> <span></span><span class=\"c9\">兮</span> <span></span>in which the first four symbols literally mean “words of Dao”, but does this mean “talking about Dao” or “the words that come out of Dao”?  It can be argued both ways due to subtleties in the meanings of the symbols, but there is a tremendous difference in meaning between the two translations.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000245": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000245",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000246": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000246",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000247": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000247",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000248": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000248",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\">In addition, there are a few symbols whose modern English meanings just don’t make sense within the context of the sentence, probably due either to transcription errors or changes in meaning over the millennia.  The English words used for these symbols are usually selected according to context.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000249": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000249",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000250": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000250",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000251": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000251",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000252": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000252",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal c1\"><b>==============================================================</b></p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000253": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000253",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000254": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000254",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal c1\"><b> </b></p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000255": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000255",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000256": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000256",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal c1\"><b>Common Terms</b></p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000257": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000257",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000258": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000258",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000259": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000259",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000260": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000260",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Because the translation itself is meant to involve minimal interpretation and explanation, some of the words and phrases that are used repeatedly need to be discussed beforehand for clarity.  Keep in mind that volumes have been written about some of these concepts – these are just brief summaries for the reader new to Daoism.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000261": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000261",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000262": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000262",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000263": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000263",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000264": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000264",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal c10\"><span class=\"c9\">道</span> Dao : most often translated as the “way”; according to various passages in the DDJ, Dao appears to be the way of nature (or the universe), the process of being in harmony with that way, the source that creates and nourishes all things, and absolute ultimate reality itself (and according to the opening lines of the first chapter, this description is completely inadequate); it is left untranslated so that readers may “fill in the blank” for themselves as they read; “the Dao” is used as little as possible because in English that implies that Dao is more of a thing than a process; Dao is sometimes referred to as “it” to avoid awkward grammar (or if it was written that way in the original Chinese), but do not think of Dao as a noun (just for fun sometime, try reading “Dao” as “Daoing”…); one exception is when “Dao of” is used (for example, “the Dao of heaven”) – this seems to be literally referring to the way heaven does things, so it is translated as “the Way of heaven”, but “Way” is capitalized to remind the reader that this is also Dao; similarly, “this Dao” seems to be referring more to “this <i>way</i> (of following Dao), and is translated “this Way”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000265": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000265",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000266": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000266",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal c15\"><span class=\"c14\"> </span></p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000267": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000267",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000268": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000268",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal c10\"><span class=\"c9\">德</span> <span></span>De : most often translated as “virtue”, “integrity”, or “(inner) power”, De is described in chapter 49 as “goodness” or “virtue” and “honesty” or “trust”; De might be infused into things when they are created by/from Dao, or something that develops when Dao is fully expressed through a person; De seems to be both the quality of being virtuous and the power that comes from being virtuous, so it might best be thought of as “the power of one’s virtue” or “the power from one’s integrity”, but it is also left untranslated so that readers may “fill in the blank” for themselves as they read</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000269": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000269",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000270": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000270",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000271": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000271",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000272": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000272",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal c10\"><span class=\"c9\">天</span> “heaven” : a complex concept, this symbol seems to have connotations of the sky, nature (including people and societies), that which controls our destinies, as well as possibly that of a celestial god-like spirit (and/or perhaps ancestral spirits)</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000273": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000273",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000274": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000274",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000275": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000275",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000276": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000276",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal c10\"><span class=\"c9\">天</span> <span></span><span class=\"c9\">地</span> “heaven and earth” : everything, the universe, all that is</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000277": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000277",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000278": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000278",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000279": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000279",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000280": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000280",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal c10\"><span class=\"c9\">天</span> <span></span><span class=\"c9\">下</span> <span></span>“the world” : literally “heaven under”, it is perhaps better thought of as “all things under heaven”; it is left as “the world” because the English grammar sometimes gets awkward using the more accurate phrase; some translate it as “the empire”, which gives the entire document a much more imperialistic and militaristic slant</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000281": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000281",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000282": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000282",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000283": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000283",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000284": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000284",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal c10\"><span class=\"c9\">萬</span> <span></span><span class=\"c9\">物</span> “ten thousand creatures” : “ten thousand” as used here does not refer to a specific number, but means “innumerable” or “myriad”; together the symbols are perhaps better thought of as “all creatures and things”</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000285": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000285",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000286": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000286",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal c10\"> </p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000287": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000287",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000288": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000288",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal c10\"><span class=\"c9\">聖</span> <span></span><span class=\"c9\">人</span> “sage” : literally “holy man”; in the DDJ, a sage is anyone who fully embodies and expresses Dao and De; as the ruling class would have been one of the few literate groups in ancient Chinese culture reading the DDJ, it seems possible that references to the way the sage does things could have also been a subtle way of saying “this is what a wise <span class=\"c5\">ruler</span> would do” (especially in chapters like 5, 57, and 66, where the sage seems to be the ruler)</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000289": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000289",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000290": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000290",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000291": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000291",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000292": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000292",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal c10\"><span class=\"c9\">常</span> “ever-constant” : while this is often translated as “eternal”, it probably had more of a sense of “constant” or “permanent” in ancient China; unfortunately “constant” doesn’t imply the enduring nature of “permanent”, nor does “permanent” imply the unchanging quality of “constant”, so “ever-constant” is used here</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000293": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000293",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000294": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000294",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000295": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000295",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000296": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000296",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal c10\"><span class=\"c9\">心</span> “heart/mind” : usually translated as either “heart” or “mind” (the symbol means both), “heart/mind” seems to be the best translation</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000297": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000297",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000298": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000298",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000299": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000299",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000300": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000300",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal c10\"><span class=\"c9\">自</span> <span></span><span class=\"c9\">然</span> “naturally so” : this has the connotation of something that happens spontaneously, without being forced (“of itself”, “of its own accord”, “on its own”); Dao is “naturally so”, and although the DDJ does not say so explicitly, presumably the sage acts “naturally so” as well</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000301": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000301",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000302": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000302",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000303": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000303",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000304": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000304",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal c10\"><span class=\"c9\">樸</span> “uncarved block” (of wood) : just as a block of wood can be carved into virtually anything, in the DDJ the “uncarved block” represents the limitless undefined potential of our original nature</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000305": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000305",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000306": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000306",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000307": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000307",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000308": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000308",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal c10\"><span class=\"c9\">無</span> <span></span><span class=\"c9\">為</span> “non-action” : not passivity or lack of action, but spontaneous action taken at the proper time according to the situation</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000309": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000309",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000310": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000310",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000311": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000311",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000312": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000312",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal c10\"><span class=\"c9\">無</span> <span></span><span class=\"c9\">事</span> <span></span>“non-interference” : to change the natural order of things as little as possible in achieving your goals</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000313": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000313",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000314": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000314",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000315": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000315",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000316": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000316",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal c10\"><span class=\"c9\">無</span> <span></span><span class=\"c9\">知</span> <span></span>“without-knowledge” : not an absence of knowledge, but a kind of understanding that does not resort to pre-conceived ideas or rules</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000317": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000317",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000318": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000318",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal c10\"><span class=\"c9\">無</span> <span></span><span class=\"c9\">名</span> “without-name” : a reminder that things, concepts, and experiences are far more than the names we give them and ultimately cannot be described with words (in contrast to the Confucians, whose goal was to find the “correct name” for everything)</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000319": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000319",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000320": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000320",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000321": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000321",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000322": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000322",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal c10\"><span class=\"c9\">無</span> <span></span><span class=\"c9\">欲</span> “without-desire” : not a total lack of desire, but desires that do not control us or our happiness; a sort of spontaneous, unattached desire</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000323": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000323",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000324": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000324",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000325": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000325",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000326": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000326",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal c10\"><span class=\"c9\">無</span> or <span class=\"c9\">無</span> <span></span><span class=\"c9\">有</span> “non-being” : the nameless absolute that is the source of all existence (“being”)</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000327": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000327",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000328": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1a2844f534b920c9/text/000000328",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p></div></div>"
        },
