            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Symbols that show up much more often in two layers but rarely in the other one are presented in the table on the following page, in the same format as the previous one.  Symbols in the “Never” sections appear about equally often in the other two layers, but not once in the indicated layer.</p></div></div>"
        },
