            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-8b1105 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-65f006 twpub-1a2844f534b920c9-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span class=\"c24\">Thus the sage plans for things to be difficult,</span></p></div></div>"
        },
